You're right, I was testing with tokens that started with numbers, so 0 didn't match anything.<p><pre><code>  SELECT * FROM users where reset_token = 0;
</code></pre>
will match the token "abc";<p><pre><code>  SELECT * FROM users where reset_token = 1;
</code></pre>
will match the token "1abc";<p><pre><code>  SELECT * FROM users where reset_token = 123;
</code></pre>
will match the token "123aasfas".
